attributes.title: AHWU 20th Anniversary Special | Achievement Hunter Weekly Update: Ep. 578 | Rooster Teeth
attributes.caption: Surprise! It's a brand-new episode of AHWU.
attributes.description: Surprise! It's a brand-new episode of AHWU, the first of 20 all-new episodes of your favorite Rooster Teeth shows that will be releasing over the next 20 weeks. What are the rest of the mystery videos? Leave your guesses in the comments. Jack, Geoff, and the whole Achievement Hunter crew are back to deliver you all the news you need to know for the week (or in this case, year), open your packages, and cause all sorts of chaos throughout the AH office. Fun fact: if we're talking numbers, this is AHWU #578. In a world where AHWU never ended, this would be AHWU #671.   || Art of the Year ► https://www.tumblr.com/ah-artcrew/700474041850527744/ah-art-crew-fashion-zinepdf?source=share || Check out All Good No Worries ► https://roosterteeth.com/channel/all-good-no-worries || More AHWU ► https://roosterteeth.com/series/ahwu

attributes.title: RT Docs: The Untold Story of Funhaus
attributes.caption: Thank you for 20 years of support! As a token of our gratitude, we've created a series of surprise videos that we'd like to share with you. Each one is our gift to you and a way to say thanks for being a part of the Rooster Teeth community. We couldn't have made it this far without you, and we look forward to many more years of making fun together!
attributes.description: Join Funhaus as they take you through their absolutely true, 100% not fake origin story and share never before seen lost footage of their time together before they were Funhaus.
attributes.display_title: RT Docs: The Untold Story of Funhaus
